resources.string:
Lolu hlelo lokusebenza lusebenzisa idatha ye-crowdsourced evela ku-OpenStreetMap ukubonisa imikhawulo yesivinini. Le datha ingase ingaphelele, inganembile, noma iphelelwe yisikhathi.

ASENZI IZIQINISEKISO mayelana nokunemba, ukwethembeka, noma ukuphelela kwanoma yiluphi ulwazi lomkhawulo wesivinini olubonisiwe.

UWUPHENDULE WEDWA UBOPHEZELO lokuthobela yonke imithetho yethrafikhi kanye nemikhawulo yesivinini ethunyelwe. Ngaso sonke isikhathi bheka izimpawu zomgwaqo ezisemthethweni njengomthombo ogunyaziwe.

Ngokusebenzisa lolu hlelo lokusebenza, uyavuma ukuthi onjiniyela, abanikeli, nabahlinzeki bedatha abamukeli ISIBOPHO sanoma yimiphi imiphumela evela ngenxa yokuthembela kulwazi olubonisiwe, okuhlanganisa kodwa kungagcini nje ngokuphulwa kwethrafikhi, izingozi, ukulimala, noma ukulimala kwanoma yiluphi uhlobo.

UNGALOKOTHI uhlanganyele nalolu hlelo lokusebenza ngenkathi ushayela. Misa ngaphambi kokuthi uqale uhambo lwakho futhi uhambe ngokuphepha uma udinga ukwenza izinguquko.

Ukuphepha kwakho nokuphepha kwabanye kuwumthwalo wakho.
